    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>μνημονεύω[d] and μνεία[b] overlap with the domain of Communication (33), since the meaning involves not only remembering but making mention of a person in prayer. It is possible, however, that the prayer would be inaudible, that is to say, silent prayer.</Content>
